      "island_trader_387861": {
        "id": "island_trader_387861",
        "name": "Island Trader",
        "emoji": "🧺",
        "description": "As you step into the shade of the thatched hut, the smell of salt, dried fish, and smoked wood wraps around you.\n\nA broad-shouldered trader with sun-bleached hair looks up from sorting nets and flashes you a quick grin.\n> New face, new canoe,” they say. “You’re either brave, lost, or both.\n\nTheir eyes flick to your empty hands.\n> Out here, the sea feeds the ones who know how to ask politely. You want to start bringing home more than stories? You’ll be needing a fishing rod.\n\nA sign reads:",
        "items": [
          {
            "itemId": "coconut_094674",
            "price": 15,
            "addedAt": 1763660406453,
            "stock": 0
          },
          {
            "itemId": "fishing_rod_667743",
            "price": 20,
            "addedAt": 1763684549085
          }
        ],
        "settings": {
          "storeownerText": "Sorry, there's a coconut shortage at the moment, none up for grabs."
        },
        "metadata": {
          "createdAt": 1763961252720,
          "lastModified": 1763961252720,
          "totalSales": 0
        }
      },
