        "name": "Lance of Ruin",
        "emoji": "<:lor:1396878903498379355>",
        "description": "The Lance of Ruin is a weapon born of ancient vengeance, its jagged crimson form crackling with a power that feels both divine and cursed.\n\nForged from the blood-stained legacy of the Crest of Lamine and wielded by the tragic hero-turned-monster Miklan, it thrums with a fury that defies fate itself. When gripped in battle, it howls with the rage of a forgotten lineage, every thrust tearing through air and flesh like a scream for justice unmet.",
