            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🪨C1 | Small Island",
              "description": "Well...there's not much here. Just some barren rocks crumbling into the ocean. \n\nBut you do see what looks like some sort of...key? It's rusted bronze, nothing particularly pretty...but it probably unlocks something somewhere...",
              "image": null,
              "clues": []
            },
