          "D1": {
            "channelId": "1400526764803100693",
            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🦈 D1 | SHARK ATTTACK",
              "description": "SHIT SHIT SHIT SHIT SHIT. THAT'S A LOTTA FUCKIN SHARKS\n\n🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈🦈\n\nYou spend so much time running away that you don't get to do anything else here. But you escape unscathed...relatively",
              "image": null,
              "clues": []
            },
            "buttons": [
