          "G1": {
            "channelId": "1400526792883699803",
            "baseContent": {
              "title": "⛈️ G1 | The Typhoon",
              "description": "A typhoon rages, localized in this corner of the map. \n\nThe waves toss you back and forth, with your boat barely staying afloat as you furiously bail water out. \n\nIn the distance, you see a brief repose: A rock, seemingly in the eye of the storm. And it looks like...there's something on it?\n\nIf you paddle hard enough, you'll be able to get there and claim  whatever is on the island. If you fail though, you'll be washed away...and who knows where you'll land.",
              "image": "https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1418593743514243193/1441178094538068048/Copilot_20251120_162321.png?ex=6920d931&is=691f87b1&hm=a6f2fbc0347f4a5b652c3f76a29d41f3bb7debd24d6fcf452ca06072525c848a&=&format=webp&quality=lossless&width=2196&height=1464",
