            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🏝️A2 | A Quiet Straight",
              "description": "The straight between your home islands is quiet. Peaceful, even, as peaceful as the open ocean can be during a journey like this. \n\nEither way, it's boring. Better set sail for something more interesting...",
