            "channelId": "1400526796100730935",
            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🦜B2 | Annoying Bird",
              "description": "A bird sits perched on the outstretched branch of a palm tree. It eyes you from the edge of the shore, almost...staring into your soul a little bit. Weird. \n\nAnyways, it looks like there's a set of dice sitting in the sand under the bird's branch. You could probably make a break for it but...you'll have to beat the bird to it first.\n\nOff into the distance, a smooth, flat rock has been set upright in the sand as if it’s marking a spot.",
              "image": null,
              "clues": []
            },
