            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🏝️ C2 | The Coastline",
              "description": "Finally! The open ocean is all yours. It looks like there are more islands to the east...including a volcano of some sort. Probably worth checking out. \n\nEither way, the open seas fill you with adrenaline and let you row faster. Either towards home, or towards adventure.",
