            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🪸F2 | Beautiful Reef",
              "description": "You're no stranger to reefs at this point, but this one takes the cake. \n\nContrasted with the ash-covered volcano, the pinks and oranges of the coral shine out of the water with an almost radiant glow. \n\nIt's absolutely beautiful. And worthless, other than for its looks.",
