            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🌋G2 | Volcano Run",
              "description": "Well, this is certainly a volcano. \n\nIt's massive, with its rolling cliffsides blanketed by ash and pumice. \n\nIf something looks this cool, surely there's something cool inside of it right? \n\nOnly way one way to find out: Make it to the center.",
              "image": null,
              "clues": []
