          "B3": {
            "channelId": "1400526853122293852",
            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🚣🏽B3 | Boat Shop",
              "description": "On this large island lies a massive shop of some sort. \n\nAn elderly lady, with pale white hair pulled back as she works, beckons over to you. \n\n> \"If you want to explore where the *real* prizes are, you'll need a better boat than that.\" \n\nShe gestures at your boat in an almost mocking manner. \n\n> \"Tell you what. Go to the volcano across the ocean, and bring me back what's in there. If you can get me that, I'll be able to make you a better boat. If you already have it, even better. \"\n\nSounds like you don't have much of a choice but to listen to her...",
              "image": "",
              "clues": []
            },
