              "description": "SHIT SHIT SHIT THAT'S A BIG ASS SHARK. \n\nAt its chomping its teeth in your general direction, you notice something. \n\nIs that...a gold tooth? Well, that's probably worth something, right?\n\nUnfortunately, there's only one way to find out...",
