            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🔭 D3 | The Viewpoint",
              "description": "Hey, this little island has a little hill on it.\n\nFrom the top, you can actually see pretty far. You can see more islands, another volcano, and some weird wildlife.\n\nUnfortunately, you can also see that you'll need a bigger, better boat to get down there. Wonder where you can get one of those...",
