            "config": {
              "title": "Retro Helicopter",
              "content": "You climb ashore and find that the volcano is way too tall to climb, and there are no other entrances other than the mouth.\n\nOff to the side you find an old helicopter with just enough fuel to get you in and out. Fortunately, you know how to fly one.\n\nTo succeed at this task, ping production **in your subs** with a screenshot of you scoring 4,500m or higher in Retro Helicopter at this link.\n\nhttps://www.coolmathgames.com/0-retro-helicopter\n\nWe should be able to tell the screenshot is from today.",
              "image": "https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1418593743514243193/1440777927124844674/helicopter_volcano.png?ex=691f6482&is=691e1302&hm=12f25460d91d08144a1ea7f8579db50a8b46568e0732bb3f86712c6d07f2a5c1&=&format=webp&quality=lossless&width=1191&height=1191"
