            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "TRICK THE BIRD",
              "content": "The bird cocks its head towards you, almost in a mocking manner. It chirps at you, figuratively and literally, mimicking your actions. \n\nYou'll never beat it in a full on race...but you might be able to out smart it if you try hard enough. \n\nTo succeed at this task, ping production in your subs with a screenshot of you scoring 6,000 or higher on Semantris Arcade Mode at this link. \n\nhttps://research.google.com/semantris/\n\nWe should be able to tell the screenshot is from today.",
              "image": ""
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
