      "the_whale_s_riddle_277419": {
        "id": "the_whale_s_riddle_277419",
        "name": "The Whale's Riddle",
        "label": "The Whale's Riddle",
        "emoji": "🐳",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "THE WHALE'S RIDDLE",
              "content": "The whale stares at you, it's eyes looking deep into your soul. \n\n\"You only get one chance to answer my riddle, so do so wisely. If you fail, you won't get to try again.\"\n\nYou nod your head,  oddly confident in yourself despite the...giant mystical whale staring you down. \n\nThe whale then gives you the following riddle:\n\n*I live where I cannot breathe*\n\n*I eat but I have no teeth*\n\n*I sing but there is no music*\n\n*What am I?*\n\nPing production *in your subs* with your answer. You may only attempt to answer the riddle on this space of the map",
              "image": ""
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "The Whale's Riddle",
            "emoji": "🐳",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": {
          "logic": "AND",
          "items": []
        },
        "coordinates": [
          "E2"
        ],
        "description": "The whale stares deep into your soul. \n\n\"You get one shot at this. If you fail, you lose your chance.\"\n\nHe then gives you the following riddle: \n\n*I live where I cannot breathe*\n\n*I eat but I have no teeth*\n\n*I sing but there is no music*\n\n*What am I?*\n\nPing production **in your subs** with your answer",
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1763961252722,
          "lastModified": 1763961252722,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": [
            "The whale stares deep into your soul. \n\n\"You get one shot at this. If you fail, you lose your chance.\"\n\nHe then gives you the following riddle: \n\n*I live where I cannot breathe*\n\n*I eat but I have no teeth*\n\n*I sing but there is no music*\n\n*What am I?*\n\nPing production **in your subs** with your answer"
