      "cave_entrance_grass_802536": {
        "id": "cave_entrance_grass_802536",
        "name": "Cave Entrance - Grass",
        "label": "Cave Entrance - Grass",
        "emoji": "☘️",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "🌿 You search the grass and...",
              "content": "> The grass stretches endlessly across the valley—lush, waist-high, and swaying with every gust of wind. There’s no way a single pair of eyes could cover it all. Fortunately, you and your companions know how to fan out like professionals.\n\nMinutes pass. The sun presses overhead. The chirping of insects is all you hear.\n\nThen—you stumble.\n\nYour foot catches on something beneath the green. Not a root, but stone. You brush aside a thick cluster of blades, revealing a rough, uneven patch of ground. Nestled between two half-buried rocks, you find it:\n\nA hole.\n\nBarely wider than your shoulders. Jagged at the edges. And dark. So, so dark.\n\nA faint, cool breeze flows from within. No sound. No light. Just the yawning promise of something vast waiting beneath.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "#3D9140"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          },
          {
            "type": "follow_up_button",
            "order": 1,
            "config": {
              "buttonId": "enter_cave_245013"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "modal",
          "button": {
            "label": "Cave Entrance - Grass",
            "emoji": "☘️",
            "style": "Primary"
          },
          "modal": {
            "keywords": [],
            "caseSensitive": false
          },
          "phrases": [
            "inspect grass",
            "inspect emerald grass",
            "inspect lush grass",
            "inspect lush emerald grass",
            "inspect the grass"
          ]
        },
        "conditions": {
          "logic": "AND",
          "items": []
        },
        "coordinates": [
          "G5"
        ],
        "description": "Cave entrance hidden here",
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1761462566174,
          "lastModified": 1761462566174,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": [
            "Cave entrance hidden here"
          ]
        }
      },
      "enter_cave_245013": {
        "id": "enter_cave_245013",
        "name": "Enter Cave",
        "label": "Enter Cave",
        "emoji": null,
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "🕳️ The Cave of the Forgotten Seal",
              "content": "> After combing the waist-high grass of the riverlands, you stumble—literally—upon it: a narrow fissure hidden beneath a tangle of overgrowth, just wide enough for a human to slip through. The ground gives a quiet groan as you descend, sliding between cold stone and roots, until the light of the world above fades behind you.\n\nAnd then… it opens.\n\nYou emerge into a cavern vast enough to swallow sound. The walls ripple outward in sweeping arcs, like the ribs of a long-dead god. The ceiling vanishes into darkness above, broken only by faint trickles of quartz light and the murmur of distant dripping water.\n\nBut something here feels… disturbed.\n\nFootprints disturb the dust. Boot scuffs. A broken lantern. Scraps of cloth snagged on stone. Whatever sanctity this place once held, it’s been trespassed.\n\nAt the far end, two massive gates await—twin discs of slate-gray alloy, fused seamlessly into the rock like the unblinking eyes of some buried titan. They hum faintly with locked power, cold and unmoving.\n\n## 🪓 The Axe Seal\nSet before the first gate stands a broad stone pedestal, waist-high and circular in shape—almost like an altar or offering table, its surface weathered by centuries of still air. Three distinct carvings are chiseled into its face, each recessed slightly into the stone as if awaiting something to be placed within:\n1. A triangular recess, its edges sharp and angular.\n2. A perfect circular depression, smooth and precise.\n3. A deep-set engraving shaped like an exotic axe.\n\n## 🗡️ The Sword Seal\nA stone pedestal stands before the second gate—flat, round, and etched with three distinct recesses:\n1. A triangular recess, its edges sharp and angular.\n2. A perfect circular depression, smooth and precise.\n3. A full-length sword-shaped carving.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "#384861"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          },
          {
            "type": "follow_up_button",
            "order": 1,
            "config": {
              "buttonId": "open_gate_907777"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          },
          {
            "type": "follow_up_button",
            "order": 2,
            "config": {
              "buttonId": "sword_pedestal_303719"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Enter Cave",
            "emoji": null,
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [],
        "description": "Prompt for the player to enter the Bandit Cave",
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1761462566174,
          "lastModified": 1761462566174,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": [
            "Prompt for the player to enter the Bandit Cave"
          ]
        }
      },
      "open_gate_907777": {
        "id": "open_gate_907777",
        "name": "Axe Pedestal",
        "label": "Axe Pedestal",
        "emoji": null,
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "🪓The Axe Pedestal Trembles...",
              "content": "> As you approach the ancient pedestal, the relics placed in the stone begin to stir—glowing with a pulsing light that syncs with the carvings in the stone.\n\nThe pedestal thrums beneath your fingertips. A deep tone echoes through the chamber, ancient and resonant. One by one, the carvings glow brighter—until a blinding pulse of light surges outward.\n\nAhead, the massive gate groans.\n\nStone grinds against stone as the seal recedes—haltingly at first, then with gathering force. Dust rains from above. A breath of warm, stale air wafts through the widening crack.\n\nAnd beyond that crack… the flicker of torchlight.\n\nThe seal is broken. The path forward lies open.\n\n```# Ping Production\nTo see what awaits you...```",
              "image": "",
              "color": "#3BA9B8"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          },
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 1,
            "config": {
              "title": "🚫 The Mechanism Remains Silent",
              "content": "> You press your hands to the stone pedestal. For a breathless moment, something stirs beneath the surface—grooves in the carvings catch the light, a faint pulse flickers through the etched channels…\n\nBut then—nothing.\n\nThe glow fades. The pedestal stills. No hum. No turning of stone. No answer.\n\nThe seal does not recognize what you've brought.\nNot yet.\n\nA weight settles into the cavern’s silence, like a door waiting for the right knock—one it has not heard in ages.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "#ff0000"
            },
            "executeOn": "false"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Axe Pedestal",
            "emoji": "🔓",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [
          {
            "id": "cond_1755426914734_cn4qd",
            "type": "item",
            "operator": "has",
            "logic": "AND",
            "itemId": "emberbrand_relic_485500"
          },
          {
            "id": "cond_1755426940170_xu60l",
            "type": "item",
            "operator": "has",
            "logic": "AND",
            "itemId": "spiral_of_echoes_350510"
          },
          {
            "id": "cond_1755426962120_0wkoj",
            "type": "item",
            "operator": "has",
            "logic": "AND",
            "itemId": "aymr_795754"
