      "sword_pedestal_303719": {
        "id": "sword_pedestal_303719",
        "name": "Sword Pedestal",
        "label": "Sword Pedestal",
        "emoji": null,
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "🗡️ The Sword Seal Activates",
              "content": "As you approach the second pedestal, the relics you’ve placed within begin to shimmer—each glowing in sync with the recesses carved into the stone.\n\nA faint vibration hums beneath your hands. The pedestal responds with a deep, resonant tone—low and steady, as if echoing through the bones of the earth itself. One by one, the recesses ignite with radiant light, culminating in a blinding flash that ripples outward.\n\nAhead, the sealed gate quivers.\n\nStone grinds in protest, then yields. The immense disc recedes with slow, grinding force, releasing a gust of stagnant, warm air. Dust rains from above as the way forward is revealed.\n\nAnd just beyond… the glint of torchlight.\n\nThe seal is broken. The sword’s path lies open.\n\n```# Ping Production\nTo see what lies beyond the seal...```",
              "image": "",
              "color": "#00ff00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          },
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 1,
            "config": {
              "title": "🚫 The Mechanism Remains Silent",
              "content": "> You press your hands to the stone pedestal. For a breathless moment, something stirs beneath the surface—grooves in the carvings catch the light, a faint pulse flickers through the etched channels…\n\nBut then—nothing.\n\nThe glow fades. The pedestal stills. No hum. No turning of stone. No answer.\n\nThe seal does not recognize what you've brought.\nNot yet.\n\nA weight settles into the cavern’s silence, like a door waiting for the right knock—one it has not heard in ages.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "#ff0000"
            },
            "executeOn": "false"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Sword Pedestal",
            "emoji": "🗡️",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [
          {
            "id": "cond_1755540376232_90rav",
            "type": "item",
            "operator": "has",
            "logic": "AND",
            "itemId": "emberbrand_relic_485500"
          },
          {
            "id": "cond_1755540404492_4xhi7",
            "type": "item",
            "operator": "has",
            "logic": "AND",
            "itemId": "spiral_of_echoes_350510"
          },
          {
            "id": "cond_1755540432692_53u92",
            "type": "item",
            "operator": "has",
            "logic": "AND",
            "itemId": "_898695"
          }
        ],
        "coordinates": [],
