            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "\"I've been planting\"",
              "content": "\"Oh! Hi Professor. You caught me off guard. I'm taking a bit of a break after gardening all day. I just added some soil to the plantar at the entrance hall. I was thinking a Rose would look nice there. All this just... helps me keep my mind off everything.\"",
