        "name": "Talk to Ingrid",
        "label": "Talk to Ingrid",
        "emoji": null,
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "Worried",
              "content": "\"Hi Professor. I am so thankful the chef stayed after everything that happened. I know most people can't eat when they are stressed, but I can't seem to stop. And now Dorothea is gone to Remire Village to speak to the new blacksmith there.... oh where's the biscuits at?\"",
