              "content": "\"What?\" Hilda snaps at you as you approach. \"I do not have the time for this right now, Professor. I was supposed to meet Lysithea at the Rhodos Coast and give her something, but I do not feel like it! Will you do it for me? It will be worth your while, I swear",
