        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1761462566175,
          "lastModified": 1761462566175,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "inspect_hawk_117877": {
        "id": "inspect_hawk_117877",
        "name": "Inspect Hawk",
        "label": "Inspect Hawk",
        "emoji": "🦅",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "Ancient Timekeeper’s Riddle",
              "content": "> You lift your gaze. Far above, the hawk circles once, twice—then dives low, cutting through the mist like an arrow of fate. It lands with uncanny precision atop a moss-covered sundial, half-buried in earth and memory.\n\nAs you approach, you notice faint lines carved into the ancient stone—weathered, but unmistakably intentional. The hawk watches you, unmoving, as if guarding something sacred.\n\nInscribed on the sundial’s surface:\n\n> _\"Eight suns from the Prime Meridian I stand,_  \n> _Neither first nor last, but held in balance by the ticking of the old world._  \n> _Your path lies not in shadows, but in the Hall of Hours,_  \n> _where each name bears a **role**, and the Eighth waits for you to claim it.\"_\n\nThe grooves in the stone seem to align with something unseen… as though expecting a name, or a choice, to be made.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "#FEE75C"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          },
          {
            "type": "follow_up_button",
            "order": 1,
            "config": {
              "buttonId": "g8_solve_time_riddle_527242"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "modal",
          "button": {
            "label": "Inspect Hawk",
            "emoji": "🦅",
            "style": "Primary"
          },
          "modal": {
            "keywords": [],
            "caseSensitive": false
          },
          "phrases": [
            "inspect hawk",
            "inspect hawks",
            "look at hawk",
            "talk to hawk",
            "hawk"
          ]
        },
        "conditions": {
          "logic": "AND",
          "items": []
        },
        "coordinates": [
          "G1"
        ],
        "description": "Lands on sundial",
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1761462566175,
          "lastModified": 1761462566175,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": [
            "Lands on sundial"
          ]
        }
      },
      "g8_solve_time_riddle_527242": {
        "id": "g8_solve_time_riddle_527242",
        "name": "Touch the Sundial",
        "label": "Touch the Sundial",
        "emoji": "🕰️",
        "style": 3,
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "⏳ The Sundial Responds",
              "content": "As your palm brushes the weathered stone, the grooves glow faintly—aligning not with the sun, but with something older. The hawk cries again, circling once overhead, then vanishes into the clouds.\n\nA compartment slides open with a soft click, revealing a small pouch of aged coins within.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "#FEE75C"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          },
          {
            "type": "give_currency",
            "order": 1,
            "config": {
              "amount": 25,
              "limit": {
                "type": "once_per_player",
                "claimedBy": []
              }
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          },
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 2,
            "config": {
              "title": "🕰️ Nothing Happens",
              "content": "You rest your hand on the sundial’s surface. The carvings remain still—quiet, inert, and cold to the touch. No glow. No sound.\n\nThe hawk watches from above, unmoving.\n\nIt seems something within you… or about you… does not align with the mechanism's ancient design.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "#ff0000"
            },
            "executeOn": "false"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Touch the Sundial",
            "emoji": "🕰️",
            "style": 3
          },
          "modal": {
            "keywords": [],
            "caseSensitive": false
          }
        },
        "conditions": [
