        "id": "aymr_795754",
        "name": "Aymr",
        "description": "A savage, relic-class battle axe forged with otherworldly design—its pale, asymmetrical head curves like a serrated nautilus shell, studded with vicious spikes and anchored to a cold, industrial haft.",
