      "_898695": {
        "id": "_898695",
        "name": "Sword of the Creator",
        "description": "An ancient, sinew-wrapped relic sword fused with divine sinew and old-world craftsmanship—its bone-pale blade coils with spinal ridges, ending in a jagged spine, while its hilt curves into clawed talons that seem half-organic, half-forged. Said to be carved from the spine of a fallen god, it awakens only in the hands of those who bear the Crest of Flames.",
