            "baseContent": {
              "title": "⚔️ D3 Officers Academy",
              "description": "The Officers Academy has a sprawling grass common area where students relax and enjoy the sun. Some are studying while others relax and enjoy the sun. It is a busy area indeed, and items are scattered about. \n\nAcross from the grassy common area are three large wooden doors.",
