          "E3": {
            "channelId": "1431901303721951333",
            "baseContent": {
              "title": "⛪ E3 Cathedral",
              "description": "Six pillars support the looming ceiling of the Cathedral. To the side, you can hear students practicing with the Choir Coordinator - and someone is certainly off key. An incredibly tall window sits at the end of the Cathedral allowing in the bright sunlight of the day. \n\nTo the side is a small room with the four Saint Statues. You see that Mercedes is praying at one now.",
              "image": "https://www.gamereactor.es/media/37/dickevorschauvon_2903723.jpg",
