          "D4": {
            "channelId": "1431901337741819998",
            "baseContent": {
              "title": "📍 D4 | Knight's Hall",
              "description": "The Knight’s Hall stands as a testament to discipline and tradition—its stone walls lined with crossed lances, crested shields, and banners from campaigns long past. Polished training dummies and sparring mats fill the center, while the scent of oiled leather and steel hangs in the air.\n\nVeteran knights murmur strategy over maps or hone blades beside the hearth, their armor clinking with every deliberate movement. A sense of quiet readiness permeates the space, as though every figure within could be summoned to battle at a moment’s notice.\n\nFelix stands talking to one of the guards, but his eyes look over when he sees you enter.\n\nOn a table in the corner sits a coin purse... ripe for the taking if someone wants it.",
              "image": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1392074397354823700/1400540677120720958/image.png?ex=688d02a6&is=688bb126&hm=873fb5c26a23447b3a41c4063682e32ac0e3572f041a943c7da609efebf595e4&",
              "clues": []
            },
            "buttons": [
              "guess_the_secret_cod_515562",
              "take_coin_purse_355561",
              "talk_to_felix_047193"
            ],
