          "C5": {
            "channelId": "1431901392552853614",
            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🚪 C5 Entrance Hall",
              "description": "The Entrance Hall - the great hub for all comings and goings of Garreg Mach. Here, families and students alike get their first look at inside the monestary. Large blue doors swing open to reveal a tiled floor and pillars supporting the roof - a room large enough that if no one were here, you could hear the echo of a pin drop.\n\nLeaning against one of the walls is Ingrid, who appears to be deeply engrossed in her book. Across from her is Lysithea, who is currently admiring one of the paintings on the walls.",
              "image": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aTnpCBnfzpE/hq720.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEhCK4FEIIDSFryq4qpAxMIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJD&rs=AOn4CLDzobESLsNGC0QKmCOMKHNwrIRBVw",
