      "open_chest_1769240718063": {
        "id": "open_chest_1769240718063",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 1,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "Despite noticing a few oddly colored tiles on the ground, which usually means something bad, you throw caution to the wind and press on.\n\nBad idea...\n\nNot 2 steps later, you press one if these tiles and immediately feel a dart pierce your neck. You begin to feel your body slow down and eventually you can barely move at all.\n\nYou have been afflicted with **SLOW**, meaning you will take a significant disadvantage on the next challenge. You must purchase a *Remedy* before beginning the challenge in order to cancel the effect.",
              "image": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452953812427083799/1462375850510127104/ffChest.png?ex=696f48a4&is=696df724&hm=4837c6245b89363c27bae90c2f627f9663c6565450caa517334e04940afe1435&",
              "color": "#7347FF"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
