      "open_chest_1770493141008": {
        "id": "open_chest_1770493141008",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "Snakes... Why did it have to be snakes...\n\nThe slithering creatures surrounding the chest are somewhat hostile, so when you attempt to open it you feel the fangs sink into your flesh.\n\nImmediately your hit with sickness, blurred vision and oozing sores. In other words, you have been hit with **VENOM**, and your current HP has been lowered to only 1.\n\nThis is by far the worst affliction, as it's fully public and cannot be cured unless you purchase a very pricey *Elixir* from the store.\n\nUntil this is done, or you lose your final HP in a boss battle (resulting in a lost vote), you will be unable to regain any HP.",
              "image": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452953812427083799/1462375850510127104/ffChest.png?ex=696f48a4&is=696df724&hm=4837c6245b89363c27bae90c2f627f9663c6565450caa517334e04940afe1435&",
              "color": "#7347FF"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Gil Chest",
            "emoji": null,
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "H7"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_226691": {
        "id": "open_chest_226691",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "That's the strangest looking creature you ever did see.\n\nIt looks like an urn... That's dancing around... With a goblin looking thing inside of it.\n\nIt's a MAGIC POT, and it doesn't seem to have any interest in attacking you.\n\nLegend has it if you manage to defeat one in a timely manner (they've been known to flee if threatened), you will be granted a full recovery of any lost HP/MP and cured if any negative status ailments.\n\nFighting this is NOT mandatory, and nothing negative happens if you fight and fail. But if you choose to fight, you MUST do it before moving on to the next room. \n\nThe challenge will require a minimum score and/or max time limit, so plan accordingly. Please use `?magic-pot` in your **subs** channel  in the Treasure Hunter server to get started.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": {
          "logic": "AND",
          "items": []
        },
        "coordinates": [
          "C7"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_1771049006492": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771049006492",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "You think you hear growling as you approach the treasure room, but when you enter everything seems somewhat normal. And it is - until you approach the chest.\n\nIt suddenly comes to life! Long arms with claws, gigantic teeth ready to rip you to shreds, and huge tongue getting a taste of it's next meal. \n\nYou have run into a dangerous **MIMIC**\n\nThese tricky foes are ready for a fight - and fight you must. Each mimic comes with a special challenge you must successfully complete in a specific way. Successful completion will result in a special reward. Failure will result in a harsh, non negotiable punishment.\n\n> To find out what your challenge is, please enter the following in your **Player Room** channel in this Treasure Hunter server to get started:\n`?4-mimic`\n\nPlease note you are forbidden from doing anything further in the treasure game until the challenge has been completed!",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "E9"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
