              "content": "You could feel something off about this treasure room before you even entered. Pure evil lurks within! You don't care about that though - there's treasure to be had!\n\nWhen you open the chest, however, you find a tablet engraved with the following:\n\n**YOU CAME FOR THE TREASURE\nBUT YOU GOT THE WORST\nNOW THE GODS FORCE YOU\nTO ACCEPT THEIR CURSE**\n\nYou are CURSED, meaning you will be randomly forced to suffer any of the other status ailments. We will use the bit to choose which one\n\nCurse itself cannot be cured, but you can cure whatever status ailment you receive with the proper item.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
