      "open_chest_1771050444608": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771050444608",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "You notice a thick mist surrounding the chest, and it really feels off. Determined to get what's inside, you press forward. Unfortunately, the moment you open it, you're hit in the face by a blast of something rancid. You immediately start babbling incoherently...\n\nYou have been afflicted with *CONFUSE*, and must speak in all public chats with a random chat punishment.\n\nThe only way to counter this is by purchasing Smelling Salts from the shop",
