      "open_chest_1771066141831": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771066141831",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "As you go to open the chest, you notice an emblem resembling a snake just above the latch. With a quick glance, you notice that the eyes of the snake begin to glow, transfixed, you stare at the eyes.\n\nYou suddenly find yourself unable to move while your skin begins to harder. You have been afflicted with **STONE**, and are unable to use open any more treasure chests for 48 hrs.\n\nThe only way to avoid this is by purchasing a *Soft* from the item shop!",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "J1"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_1771066204348": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771066204348",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "Sitting atop the treasure chest is a dusty old chalice. You pick it up and clean it off, and then notice a small stream of water pouring from a crack in the wall. You just so happen to be parched, so why not have a drink.\n\nYou hold the cup under the water, then take a big sip...\n\nPOOF\n\nYou suddenly find yourself only a couple inches tall, and craving flies. You have been afflicted with **FROG**, and must now change either your PFP or Name for the remainder of the season!\n\nPurchasing a *Maiden's Kiss* will allow you to cancel the effect, but where's the fun in that?",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "A2"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_1771066261680": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771066261680",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "No sooner do you open the chest than a cloud of green crud hits you in the face. You immediately begin feeling sick and vomiting.\n\nYou have been **POISONED** and if you don't act fast, you will lose HALF of your remaining HP!\n\nYou have one hour to buy an *Antidote* or you will be in a world of hurt!",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "F3"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_1771066327223": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771066327223",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "Opening the chest reveals a lone scroll and nothing else. Of course, what kind of adventurer would you be if you didn't at least try to read it?\n\nA smart one for starters...\n\nAs soon as you say the last word you see everything around you getting larger by the second. Or are you shrinking?\n\nYou have been afflicted with **SMALL**, meaning your power has been significantly reduced. You will suffer a severe challenge disadvantage in the next challenge you complete (sitting out won't save you - it just delays it). You can cure this by buying and using a *Cornucopia* within the next 24 hrs!",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "H4"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_1771066395854": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771066395854",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "As you enter the treasure room, a breeze comes blowing in and extinguishes your torch. Unable to see anything, you try to feel your way to the chest, but its no use. You have been afflicted by **DARKNESS**, meaning your vote will be public at the next tribal you attend.\n\nIn order to cancel the effect, you need to purchase *Eye Drops* from the vendor BEFORE that tribal begins!",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "I4"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_1771066457342": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771066457342",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "What appears to be a normal chest is anything but. Inside is not a treasure, but a small (but very pretty) flower. Curious, you pluck it out and give it a sniff. Bad choice\n\nTurns out the flower was highly toxic, and the poison within has afflicted you with **SILENCE**, and made you unable to cast any type of spell or use any skills for 48 hrs - including summons.\n\nYou need to buy an *Echo Screen* to remove the effect",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "A6"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_1771066598479": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771066598479",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "The decomposing corpse in front of the chest would normally deter wary travellers from getting closer, but you're a special case. But perhaps you should've checked to make sure the corpse was actually, you know, fully dead before continuing. It bites into your leg, and you suddenly find yourself craving human flesh.\n\nYou are now a **ZOMBIE**, meaning any and all attempts to heal you in the next 48 hrs will result in you instantly losing all HP. Oh yeah - your zombie state will be revealed to your party. The only way to reverse this is with a *Remedy*.\n\nUnlike other afflictions, though, this one CAN be a blessing if played properly. While potions and cure spells hurt you, damage actually can heal you. For every vote you receive in the 48 hrs (if you don't use the remedy), you will be healed for 1 HP up to your maximum.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "J7"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_1771066652165": {
        "id": "open_chest_1771066652165",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "You open the chest and...",
              "content": "The anticipation of opening the chest overwhelms you, so when you hear the click as you pull the lid up, you think nothing of it. You definitely feel the dart enter your neck though - but only for a second.\n\nYou become stiff, then unable to move or even talk. You triggered a **PARALYSIS** trap, which prevents you from talking in any public chat or to open any chests for 24 hrs.\n\nThe only way to counter this is by buying and using a *Remedy* from the shop.",
              "image": "",
              "color": "FFFF00"
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "🪙",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": [],
        "coordinates": [
          "D10"
        ],
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": []
        }
      },
      "open_chest_346940": {
        "id": "open_chest_346940",
        "name": "Open Chest",
        "label": "Open Chest",
        "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
        "style": "Primary",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "",
              "content": "You think you hear growling as you approach the treasure room, but when you enter everything seems somewhat normal. And it is - until you approach the chest.\n\nIt suddenly comes to life! Long arms with claws, gigantic teeth ready to rip you to shreds, and huge tongue getting a taste of it's next meal. \n\nYou have run into a dangerous **MIMIC**\n\nThese tricky foes are ready for a fight - and fight you must. Each mimic comes with a special challenge you must successfully complete in a specific way. Successful completion will result in a special reward. Failure will result in a harsh, non negotiable punishment.\n\nTo find out what your challenge is, enter the following command:\n\n?mimic-three\n\n\nPlease note you are forbidden from doing anything further in the treasure game until the challenge has been completed!",
              "image": ""
            },
            "executeOn": "true"
          }
        ],
        "trigger": {
          "type": "button",
          "button": {
            "label": "Open Chest",
            "emoji": "<:ff_chest:1462821702278058055>",
            "style": "Primary"
          }
        },
        "conditions": {
          "logic": "AND",
          "items": []
        },
        "coordinates": [
          "D4"
        ],
        "description": "You think you hear growling as you approach the treasure room, but when you enter everything seems somewhat normal. And it is - until you approach the chest.\n\nIt suddenly comes to life! Long arms with claws, gigantic teeth ready to rip you to shreds, and a huge tongue getting a taste of it's next meal. \n\nYou have run into a dangerous **MIMIC**\n\nThese tricky foes are ready for a fight - and fight you must. Each mimic comes with a special challenge you must successfully complete in a specific way. Successful completion will result in a special reward. Failure will result in a harsh, non negotiable punishment.\n\nTo find out what your challenge is, enter the following command:\n\n?mimic-three\n\n\nPlease note you are forbidden from doing anything further in the treasure game until the challenge has been completed!",
        "metadata": {
          "createdBy": null,
          "createdAt": 1772445052840,
          "lastModified": 1772445052840,
          "usageCount": 0,
          "tags": [
            "You think you hear growling as you approach the treasure room, but when you enter everything seems somewhat normal. And it is - until you approach the chest.\n\nIt suddenly comes to life! Long arms with claws, gigantic teeth ready to rip you to shreds, and a huge tongue getting a taste of it's next meal. \n\nYou have run into a dangerous **MIMIC**\n\nThese tricky foes are ready for a fight - and fight you must. Each mimic comes with a special challenge you must successfully complete in a specific way. Successful completion will result in a special reward. Failure will result in a harsh, non negotiable punishment.\n\nTo find out what your challenge is, enter the following command:\n\n?mimic-three\n\n\nPlease note you are forbidden from doing anything further in the treasure game until the challenge has been completed!"
          ]
        }
      },
